<figureCitation id="6506E855256F05F69B19674F64CD2E63" captionStart="Figure 1" captionStartId="F1" captionText="Figure 1. Holotype of Pyropia plicata sp. nov. (WELT A A 032582). Scale bar = 5 cm." httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/10245" pageId="2" pageNumber="19">Figure 1</figureCitation>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
